data.description: Stunning three bedroom, two bath home that offers the perfect blend of modern design and open living space. Located in a desirable neighborhood, this property is sure to impress all of your future guests. The open floor plan seamlessly connects the living, dining and kitchen areas, creating a sense of spaciousness and facilitating easy flow for entertaining and everyday living. Natural light floods the conveniently located near Sarasota Trailhead, Highway 86 and great dining. Modern design, open living space, and desirable location, this home will not last! Assumable FHA low interest loan available for qualified buyers.
